snippet.title: Frozen Below: Arctic Expedition - Official Reveal Trailer -  New upcoming Horror Game 2024
snippet.description:
Dear Explorer,

we are still exploring the cold desert and are finally able to share our first teaser trailer to you guys. It's been a while since we started this journey and are happy to get finally the first moving scenes out into the public.

If you have any further questions or suggestions, feel free to discuss them with us on our https://discord.gg/4JnHTzDk.

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2397240/Frozen_Below_Arctic_Expedition/
